thread.title: Strongpoint Cash Security selected as supplier of CIT-solutions to Sberbank in Russia
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Strongpoint Cash Security selected as supplier of CIT-solutions to Sberbank in Russia | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Strongpoint Cash Security selected as supplier of CIT-solutions to Sberbank in Russia
text:
Oct 15 Strongpoint ASA :
* Strongpoint Cash Security has been selected as the sole supplier of CIT-solutions to Sberbank in Russia
* Signing of a frame agreement and possible first deliveries is estimated to take place in Q4
Source text: bit.ly/1LbJ0Ox
 (Gdynia Newsroom)
